parameters: Nothing like a good, big custard doughnut~\! Wouldn’t you agree?
You know, we’re flatmates.\! We should take this chance to get to know each other better!\!
Though today I just wanna talk about myself if that’s ok!
Is there anything you wanna know about me?
I don’t know...\! Why don’t you talk about your hometown?
Hmm... A bit cliché but a good start!\! My hometown is on a small island near Illus.\! It’s
kind of an international community.\! Oh! It’s also a pretty big city if I do say so myself!
Yeah!\! Though, everyone keeps saying my hometown is not a city because it’s too small.\!
My mom’s from a much larger city, and decided to stay in my hometown when she got
married because of how quaint it was...
She’s the best!\! Although kinda lazy sometimes...
Should give her a call this week.
Oh my gosh!\! I’m sorry.\! That was a bit insensitive.
No, it’s fine.\!  You should talk about her and enjoy her while she’s still with you.
...Roz.\! Thank you for going out of your way to comfort me.\!
Sorry, but I want to be alone for a bit.
Oh...\! Um, not a problem.\! You can count on me for anything!
Oh wow!\! It's really packed huh...
Are we gonna be able to grab a seat?
M-maybe we can just grab something to go and~
MOOOOOOMOOOOOO!!\! How can you ignore your bestest friend?!\!
Mizuho.\! Drop it.\! Let's eat at home.
Awww~\! Don't be like that!\! We brought the newest
resident over to eat at your prestigeous cafe~
Sigh.\! You know you owe me a ton of money right?\! You have
no right to ask me any favors.
Ehehehe...\! W-why don't we forget about that for a
bit, and just seat us for today so Rozzy here can try your
Sigh...\! I'll see what I can do...
See?\! I got us a table!\! Let's gooo!
Pssst.\! Sigrun.\! Are Mizuho and her really best friends?
Y-yeah.\! They have an interesting friendship.\! They've
known each other since they were little girls...
Uaaaa~\! I'm so fullll~\! That was so good~
I couldn't eat properly sitting next to the kitchen.\!
Could you try not to eat into our savings when we eat out?
Oh Siggy! We had to splurge a bit to have a welcome lunch
Oh, you guys spent so much on my account. I'm sorry...\!
Don't worry~\! Now, why don't we head out and continue sightseeing?\! We can head
on over to the East side of town or straight to Vigil Castle!\! Your call!
Oh! Momo!\! Your food was great!\! Thank you!
Thanks!\! Listen, you seem like an honest gal, unlike
Mizuho.\! You're welcome to come over and buy stuff from
my cafe.\! I'll give you special treatment.
Oh, thanks!\! I'll be sure to come back!
I look forward to your business~
Take us where you'd like to go, Rozzy!
Haven't been here in a while, but this place is always packed.
I fulfilled my end of the bargain, now where are the documents?
Oh!\! I was just, uh, continuing the spy roleplay...
A-ah!\! S-sorry, I totally forgot.\! H-here's the copies of the documents I found on Vigil Castle...
Hey...\! Are you sure this is ok?
Huh?\! Yeah!\! Totally!\! These were just lying about in a pile of literary items we haven't classified or
put up.\! It has to be reviewed by the head librarian but she seems to have not touched it
even though it seems like it's been donated to the library more than a few years ago.
Huh...\! That's pretty odd.\! I really appreciate this, Kashima.
No problem!\! The doughnut is a good exchange for this information~
Oh, fudge!\! Look at the time!\! I'm gonna be late!\! Roz-chan, I'm sorry, but I have to run!\!
See you later and thanks for the doughnut!
Wish she could've hung around a bit more.\! Oh well, let's see here...
Today I could not sleep, which is why I find myself at the wee hours of the night writing this journal
entry.\! Nefertiti...\! The queen of the sands.\! I haven't seen her in years.\! Does she think I'm a
failure?\! I failed my people at their hour of need.
Instead of returning, I stay here, wallowing in self-pity.\! I cannot return however.\! How could I?\!
Besides, I still have to make that man pay.\! I will destroy Arc.\! Somehow, I know he will find his
way to me.\! I'm sorry, Rota, Nefertiti, and my captain.\! I can only watch from afar.
Perhaps, Rota was right.\! Maybe vengeance will consume me one day.\! I hope I never get to that.\! I still
have a daughter to raise.\! For those who gave their lives away, I won-"
It stops there...\! I should bring this all to Hildr.\! Maybe she might be able to recollect something.

Thanks for wanting to hang out with moo!
You’re super fun to chill with I think!
Everything going well with library work?
Though to be honest...\! I’m hoping the day I can quit comes soon...
...Roz-san.\! Do you have a dream you want to fulfill?
Hmm...\! I’m still discovering myself, but I do want to be someone that makes others happy.\!
One of my top goals is to be the ultimate housewife!
What’s better than working and staying at home?\! Cooking for your significant

W-well, people do say I take after my mom a lot...

Maybe one day you’ll trust me enough with!
You’ll be a great wife someday, Roz-san.
